Package: amortr
Type: Package
Title: Debt amortization schedules.
Version: 0.1
Date: 2024-05-17
Author: Miguel Fabián Salazar
Maintainer: Miguel Fabián Salazar <miguel@fabiansalazar.es>
Description: amortr includes a collection of debt amortization schedules calculation functions. Underlying functions are written in C++ and linked using Rcpp bindings in order to be optimal for use in large parallelized computations.
